{"tid":1691152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"除機場快綫外 港鐵各綫下周一至五晚上11時半收車","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T14:14:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e84dd61d6457c90de21b8ef7efe3242439c38bbe","tid":1691152,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港鐵指早前多個港鐵車站設施持續被人蓄意破壞，在港鐵人員努力下，各項設施的復修進度已有改善。公司一直密切監察鐵路設施再次被破壞的風險，留意到在剛過去一個星期，平日風險狀況有所下降。因應復修工作進度及與相關政府部門最新進行的風險評估，下星期一至五(十一月四日至八日)各鐵路綫(機場快綫除外)、輕鐵及港鐵巴士的服務將於晚上十一時半結束。<br />\n<br />\n由於提早結束服務安排會因應實際情況仍可能需要維持一段時間，港鐵希望預早公佈未來五天的安排，以便乘客計劃行程。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於周末的風險狀況仍然較平日為高，因此下星期六、日(十一月九日至十日)的服務結束時間仍然維持在晚上十時。<br />\n<br />\n公司會繼續監察最新的風險狀況，並與相關政府部門進行風險評估，假如風險增加或再有鐵路設施被破壞，公司有可能因應情況而縮短服務時間。若列車或車站服務需要作出調整，公司會透過港鐵網頁、MTR Mobile、車站和列車廣播，以及傳媒發放有關資訊，請乘客出行前留意最新的服務資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com?refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%3Frefer%3DShare&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=e70ab181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%3Frefer%3DShare&h=a0778bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com?refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"d9cebe5fa86e652b3ef42d5c1945109a4a6e9f93","tid":1691152,"uid":305631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:10:10.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢咪算囉"},{"pid":"ac1e05ee69af138757962898a109dd44bd2df861","tid":1691152,"uid":169079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:10:25.000Z","msg":"比商家酒吧佬屌到11點半先宵禁？"},{"pid":"f6c807342f953fea0d387c0f78b0b7373e60c5ed","tid":1691152,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a15c9b04506358fc9ce6f07138fd82d594495e","tid":1691152,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"已經接近回復正常了<br />\n好波<br />\n真係好彩啲暴徒冇亂拋雜物入嗰啲架空路軌<br />\n如果唔係工都唔使返<br />\n我仲要儲錢買樓<br />\n咪煩到我呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951fd262b9d2199eebf6faeb7bd10e71f300877d","tid":1691152,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:12:35.000Z","msg":"好明顯客量少左四成，咪拉長個服務時間囉"},{"pid":"23da1c48e10aeb9584b02328b757fe8cf5c07b20","tid":1691152,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:14:08.000Z","msg":"留意到在剛過去一個星期，平日風險狀況有所下降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}